overview: Featuring AVN's Best New Starlet of 2002, Nikita Denise. The first episode in a new series, this visual diary explores the featured performer in five "art-core" scenes of stark sexuality. all this is set against the dark musings of a photographer, portrayed by Nick Manning, and featuring Playboy Centerfold Elke Jeinsen. Each installment focuses on a single female adult star.
title: Lost Angels: Nikita Denise
